main event: An unidentified aerial object was reported sighted in Blacklick, Ohio, on June 13, 1966.
interesting points: The object was observed to have varied courses during its sighting,Weather conditions during the sighting included clouds,The witness described the object as being a solid light,It was estimated that the object was pretty fast in motion,The report concluded there was insufficient data for evaluation.
witness description: The witness is a 26-year-old female who reported the sighting with assistance from her husband.
